## Limitations

The report is based on available data up to October 2023, and the rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic means that new strategies and findings may have emerged since then. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may not capture the full global perspective on the issue. The findings are also limited to the articles and studies that were accessible and reviewed during the research process.

